{
  "name": "🔔🔄 Automação Diários TCM/TCE - COM LOOP ATÉ 12H",
  "description": "Tenta encontrar diário desde 8h até 12h. Se não achar, continua tentando a cada 30min",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "days": 1
            }
          ],
          "triggerAtHour": 8,
          "triggerAtMinute": 0,
          "timezone": "America/Belem"
        }
      },
      "name": "⏰ Cron - 8h Diariamente",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.cron",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [250, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Iniciar tentativa\nreturn {\n  tentativa: 1,\n  horaInicio: new Date().toISOString(),\n  tempoLimite: 12 * 60 * 60 * 1000 // 12 horas em ms\n};"
      },
      "name": "📊 Inicializar Contador de Tentativas",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [450, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://tcm.ioepa.com.br/busca/",
        "options": {
          "headers": {
            "User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36"
          }
        }
      },
      "name": "🌐 Scrape TCM",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.1,
      "position": [650, 100]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://www.tcepa.tc.br/diario-oficial",
        "options": {
          "headers": {
            "User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36"
          }
        }
      },
      "name": "🌐 Scrape TCE",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.1,
      "position": [650, 450]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "claude-opus-4-6",
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "Analise este HTML da página de busca do TCM/Pará e extraia:\n1. **data**: Data do diário mais recente em formato YYYY-MM-DD\n2. **url_pdf**: URL completa para download do PDF\n3. **titulo**: Título ou número do diário\n4. **descricao**: Breve descrição\n\nSe não encontrar, retorne data como null.\n\nRESPONDA APENAS EM JSON:\n{\"data\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\", \"url_pdf\": \"https://...\", \"titulo\": \"...\", \"descricao\": \"...\"}\n\nHTML:\n{{ $node[\"Scrape TCM\"].json.body.substring(0, 5000) }}",
              "role": "user"
            }
          ]
        },
        "maxTokens": 600
      },
      "name": "🤖 Claude - Analisar TCM",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [850, 100]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "claude-opus-4-6",
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "Analise este HTML da página de diários do TCE/Pará e extraia:\n1. **data**: Data do diário mais recente em formato YYYY-MM-DD\n2. **url_pdf**: URL completa para download do PDF\n3. **titulo**: Título ou número do diário\n4. **descricao**: Breve descrição\n\nSe não encontrar, retorne data como null.\n\nRESPONDA APENAS EM JSON:\n{\"data\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\", \"url_pdf\": \"https://...\", \"titulo\": \"...\", \"descricao\": \"...\"}\n\nHTML:\n{{ $node[\"Scrape TCE\"].json.body.substring(0, 5000) }}",
              "role": "user"
            }
          ]
        },
        "maxTokens": 600
      },
      "name": "🤖 Claude - Analisar TCE",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [850, 450]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "let tcmData = { orgao: 'TCM', data: null, url_pdf: null, titulo: null };\nlet tceData = { orgao: 'TCE', data: null, url_pdf: null, titulo: null };\n\ntry {\n  const tcmMsg = $node['Claude - Analisar TCM'].json.message.content;\n  tcmData = { ...tcmData, ...JSON.parse(tcmMsg) };\n} catch(e) { console.log('TCM parse error'); }\n\ntry {\n  const tceMsg = $node['Claude - Analisar TCE'].json.message.content;\n  tceData = { ...tceData, ...JSON.parse(tceMsg) };\n} catch(e) { console.log('TCE parse error'); }\n\nreturn [tcmData, tceData];"
      },
      "name": "📝 Parse Respostas",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1050, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "search",
        "table": "diarios",
        "filterBy": {
          "fields": [{ "name": "orgao", "operator": "is", "value": "TCM" }]
        },
        "options": { "limit": 1, "sort": { "field": "data", "direction": "descending" } }
      },
      "name": "📊 Get Última Data TCM",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1250, 100]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "search",
        "table": "diarios",
        "filterBy": {
          "fields": [{ "name": "orgao", "operator": "is", "value": "TCE" }]
        },
        "options": { "limit": 1, "sort": { "field": "data", "direction": "descending" } }
      },
      "name": "📊 Get Última Data TCE",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1250, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const tcmNovo = $input.all()[0].json;\nconst tceNovo = $input.all()[1].json;\nconst ultimaTcm = $node['Get Última Data TCM'].json?.records?.[0]?.data;\nconst ultimaTce = $node['Get Última Data TCE'].json?.records?.[0]?.data;\n\nconst tcmTemNovo = tcmNovo[0].data && (!ultimaTcm || tcmNovo[0].data > ultimaTcm);\nconst tceTemNovo = tceNovo[1].data && (!ultimaTce || tceNovo[1].data > ultimaTce);\n\nreturn {\n  tcm: { ...tcmNovo[0], novo: tcmTemNovo },\n  tce: { ...tceNovo[1], novo: tceTemNovo },\n  temNovo: tcmTemNovo || tceTemNovo,\n  timestamp: new Date().toISOString()\n};"
      },
      "name": "🔍 Comparar Datas",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1450, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": [
            { "condition": "custom expression", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.temNovo }}" }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "✅ Encontrou Novo?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1650, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.url_pdf }}",
        "options": { "response": { "response": { "type": "arraybuffer" } } }
      },
      "name": "⬇️ Download PDF TCM",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.1,
      "position": [1850, 50]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tce.url_pdf }}",
        "options": { "response": { "response": { "type": "arraybuffer" } } }
      },
      "name": "⬇️ Download PDF TCE",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.1,
      "position": [1850, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "file",
        "method": "upload",
        "bucket": "diarios",
        "fileName": "tcm_{{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.data }}.pdf",
        "fileContent": "={{ $node['Download PDF TCM'].json.body }}"
      },
      "name": "☁️ Upload TCM",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2050, 50]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "file",
        "method": "upload",
        "bucket": "diarios",
        "fileName": "tce_{{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tce.data }}.pdf",
        "fileContent": "={{ $node['Download PDF TCE'].json.body }}"
      },
      "name": "☁️ Upload TCE",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2050, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "insert",
        "table": "diarios",
        "rows": {
          "values": [
            { "key": "orgao", "value": "TCM" },
            { "key": "data", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.data }}" },
            { "key": "titulo", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.titulo }}" },
            { "key": "arquivo", "value": "tcm_{{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.data }}.pdf" },
            { "key": "url_original", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.url_pdf }}" }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "💾 Inserir TCM",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2250, 50]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "insert",
        "table": "diarios",
        "rows": {
          "values": [
            { "key": "orgao", "value": "TCE" },
            { "key": "data", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tce.data }}" },
            { "key": "titulo", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tce.titulo }}" },
            { "key": "arquivo", "value": "tce_{{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tce.data }}.pdf" },
            { "key": "url_original", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tce.url_pdf }}" }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "💾 Inserir TCE",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2250, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "insert",
        "table": "notifications",
        "rows": {
          "values": [
            { "key": "msg", "value": "✅ Diário {{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.novo ? 'TCM' : 'TCE' }} atualizado! - {{ $now.format('DD/MM/YYYY HH:mm') }}" },
            { "key": "read", "value": false },
            { "key": "tipo_notificacao", "value": "diario" }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "🔔 Notificar Sucesso",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2450, 100]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "insert",
        "table": "diarios_log",
        "rows": {
          "values": [
            { "key": "orgao", "value": "AMBOS" },
            { "key": "status", "value": "sucesso" },
            { "key": "data_verificada", "value": "={{ $now.format('YYYY-MM-DD') }}" },
            { "key": "mensagem", "value": "✅ SUCESSO! Diários encontrados às {{ $now.format('HH:mm') }}" }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "📝 Log Sucesso",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2450, 250]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const agora = new Date();\nconst horaAtual = agora.getHours();\nconst minutoAtual = agora.getMinutes();\n\nif (horaAtual >= 12) {\n  return {\n    continua: false,\n    motivo: 'Passou das 12h - parando tentativas',\n    horaAtual: `${horaAtual}:${minutoAtual < 10 ? '0' : ''}${minutoAtual}`\n  };\n}\n\nreturn {\n  continua: true,\n  proximaTentativa: '30 minutos',\n  horaAtual: `${horaAtual}:${minutoAtual < 10 ? '0' : ''}${minutoAtual}`\n};"
      },
      "name": "⏰ Checar Hora (< 12h?)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1650, 450]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": [
            { "condition": "custom expression", "value": "={{ $node['Checar Hora (< 12h?)'].json.continua }}" }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "❓ Continuar Tentando?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1850, 450]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Aguardar 30 minutos antes de próxima tentativa\nreturn new Promise((resolve) => {\n  setTimeout(() => {\n    resolve({ aguardou: '30 minutos', proximaTentativa: new Date().toISOString() });\n  }, 30 * 60 * 1000); // 30 minutos\n});"
      },
      "name": "⏳ Aguardar 30min",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2050, 400]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "insert",
        "table": "diarios_log",
        "rows": {
          "values": [
            { "key": "orgao", "value": "AMBOS" },
            { "key": "status", "value": "sem_atualizacao" },
            { "key": "data_verificada", "value": "={{ $now.format('YYYY-MM-DD') }}" },
            { "key": "mensagem", "value": "🔄 Nenhum novo - Tentativa às {{ $now.format('HH:mm') }} - Próxima em 30min" }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "📝 Log Retry",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1850, 600]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "insert",
        "table": "diarios_log",
        "rows": {
          "values": [
            { "key": "orgao", "value": "AMBOS" },
            { "key": "status", "value": "erro" },
            { "key": "data_verificada", "value": "={{ $now.format('YYYY-MM-DD') }}" },
            { "key": "mensagem", "value": "⏰ Passou das 12h - Parando automação. Nenhum novo encontrado." }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "📝 Log Parado 12h",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2050, 500]
    }
  ],
